data.description: Very desirable 3 Bedroom 2 bath 2 story townhome interior end unit  located in the Prairie View in Crown Point. Large main living area leading to kitchen with breakfast bar. Large eat-in kitchen has ample storage space, main floor laundry, fenced patio and 2 car garage. Completely remodeled in 2015.  Roof replaced in 2016. Bedrooms and baths recently repainted. Newer flooring in living room since remodeled. Convenient guest/resident parking directly behind unit.  Close to downtown, shopping, restaurants and I-65. HOA maintains lawn care and snow removal.  Seller will provide 1 year home warranty.
